From 886e32c41976efe48d6590f33d292f464b6774da Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: dsalinas <dsalinas@amd.com>
Date: Fri, 8 May 2026 17:41:04 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] [rocprofiler] Migrate from FindHIP MODULE to find_package(hip
 CONFIG)

Replace find_package(HIP REQUIRED MODULE) with find_package(hip CONFIG)
+ enable_language(HIP) in rocprofiler samples and legacy test files.
Also replace legacy FindHIP macros with CMake-native equivalents:
  - hip_add_executable() -> add_executable() + target_link_libraries(hip::device)
  - HIP_SOURCE_PROPERTY_FORMAT 1 -> LANGUAGE HIP

hipconfig and hipcc are no longer required for these builds; HIP is
discovered via hip-config.cmake which is built and installed by TheRock.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 projects/rocprofiler/samples/CMakeLists.txt   | 26 ++++-------
 .../featuretests/profiler/CMakeLists.txt      | 44 +++++++------------
 .../featuretests/tracer/CMakeLists.txt        | 26 ++++-------
 .../tests-v2/microbenchmarks/CMakeLists.txt   | 19 +++-----
 4 files changed, 40 insertions(+), 75 deletions(-)

